        I am involved throughout the full lifecycle of the transaction, from
        structuring and negotiations to closing and post-closing matters.
      </p>
      <p>
        Being qualified in both Italy and Spain allows me to anticipate cross-border
        issues early and to coordinate efficiently with local and international
        advisors within Pavia e Ansaldo’s platform.
      </p>
