      </p>

      <p>
        <strong>Do you only work with Italian or Spanish clients?</strong><br />
        No. I also advise international investors involved in transactions with an
        Italian or Spanish component.
      </p>

      <p>
        <strong>At what stage should a lawyer be involved?</strong><br />
        Ideally from the structuring phase. Early involvement often prevents
        execution and governance issues later in the process.
      </p>

      <p>
        <strong>Do you assist after closing?</strong><br />
        Yes. Post-closing integration and day-to-day corporate matters are a material
        part of my practice.
